  "componentDescriptions": {
    "ListItem": "Item individual. States: default/hover/selected/focused/disabled. Density: compact (32) / default (40) / comfortable (56). Marker + label + description + trailing slots.\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <li> semantic\n• Selected: aria-selected o aria-current\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Tab (nav/action types)\n\nWCAG 2.2 AA.",
    "List": "Lista ordenada/unordered/descripción/nav/action. Type determina semantic HTML + a11y pattern. Density: compact/default/comfortable. Dividers: none/between (entre items) / all (wrap completo).\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• unordered/ordered: <ul>/<ol> native\n• description: <dl><dt><dd>\n• nav: role='list' dentro de <nav>\n• action: role='menu' con arrow key nav\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Dependiente del Type\n\nTokens: 18, prefijo lst-.\nWCAG 2.2 AA.\n\nScope: listas semantic (ul/ol), description lists (term/definition), navigation menus, action menus (overflow).\n\nPara tablas de datos usa DataGrid. Para listas expandibles con jerarquía usa TreeView."
  },
  "variableBindings": {
    "lst/compact/h": "sizing/32",
    "lst/default/h": "sizing/40",
